{"tid":2456463,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"許樹昌污蔑中國疫苗！！首針有不良反應者不應再接種","createTime":"2021-03-22T03:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T03:21:51.000Z","uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0a97eea1abeb30402714e3b032bf964e1c54e5be","tid":2456463,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"政府專家顧問、中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌在本台節目表示，市民接種第二劑新冠疫苗的反應一般會較大，假如打第一劑後曾有風癩及呼吸困難等反應，不應接種第二劑。 <br />\n<br />\n對於港大計劃招募市民參與混合接種新冠疫苗計劃，即混合接種BioNTech(復必泰)及科興疫苗，許樹昌指，現時未有相關大型研究，最重要是市民過往無對疫苗過敏，假如有市民感到好奇，都可以嘗試參與計劃。他又指，日前有市民接種復必泰疫苗後出現抽搐暈倒的情況，相信是太驚及緊張的迷走神經反應，與疫苗本身無關。"},{"pid":"1a9df1e5d80ecaa01b861274691806f422ba5429","tid":2456463,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/130841220_705751243422255_1579175572181644772_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=uH403Cd-6hMAX_I9Eoa&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg6-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=fb7b378cf504b8d5fb765444140e7d14&amp;oe=607C6247\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F130841220_705751243422255_1579175572181644772_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DuH403Cd-6hMAX_I9Eoa%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg6-1.fna%26tp%3D14%26oh%3Dfb7b378cf504b8d5fb765444140e7d14%26oe%3D607C6247&h=db59406b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2b06cdf3be2c3f65493d826df6c97791fbfae13","tid":2456463,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T03:21:51.000Z","msg":"叫人打咁多次係咪痴撚線"}]}